Question: An image features a collage of three similar skincare products displayed vertically.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/236x/a1/c7/78/a1c778f466ee8f95064147b0ac862706.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image feature a collage of skincare products?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image feature a collage of skincare products?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many skincare products are displayed in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many skincare products are displayed in the image?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} == 3')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} == 3')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
